entry.title: One of America's Favorite Generals Leads the Niger Coup
entry.content: Brig. Gen. Moussa Salaou Barmou, long courted by Washington as a partner against Islamist extremism, has emerged as the main diplomatic channel between the U.S. and the junta.

entry.title: Returning Ukrainian Refugees Say There's No Place Like Home
entry.content: Those who fled the country because of the war with Russia are returning, citing family reunification as a primary reason.
